In this season our team uses srx encoders with spark max motor controllers. Our encoders are connected to left and right front controllers’ data port and they are correctly mounted (due to the green light). We are able to read data from encoders when we are using our custom codes but sysid is not reading any data from encoders and outputs 0.

encoder1536×2048 372 KB

As you can see encoder is mounted correctly

sysid1920×1440 347 KB

This is our sysid configuration. When we deploy the config, we get these lines in deploy status tab:

Robot slowly speeds up when we run quasistatic tests , but at the end of the test, sysid reads encoder data 0.

Can someone help?
